  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is a problem in convening the council tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A complicated situation has arisen in the special convening of Parliament tomorrow (15th) Friday.",
        "The next session of the parliamentary session should be held on the 19th. However, due to the decision taken in the meeting of the party leaders, it was decided to hold an urgent meeting tomorrow (15).",
        "However, if the council is to be convened in such manner, a special gazette notification shall be published. It can also be known that it should be published for 24 hours."
      ],
